{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|of a person or animal}} to be [[hot]]\n#: {{uxi|fr|J'ai chaud.|I'm hot.}}\n# {{lb|fr|informal|figuratively}} to have a [[near miss]]\n#: {{syn|fr|l'échapper belle}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|Ouf, t'as '''eu chaud''' !|Damn, that was a [[close call]]!}}\n\n====Usage notes====\nIn the second sense, only used in the {{m|fr|passé composé}}.\n\n====Conjugation====\n* see {{m|fr|avoir}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":["l'échapper belle"],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":false}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/avoir#French\" title=\"avoir\">avoir</a> <a href=\"/wiki/chaud#French\" title=\"chaud\">chaud</a></strong></span>\n</p><ol><li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\">of a person or animal</span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to be <a href=\"/wiki/hot\" title=\"hot\">hot</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">J'ai chaud.</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">I'm hot.</span></span></dd></dl></li>\n<li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#informal\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">informal</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figuratively</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to have a <a href=\"/wiki/near_miss\" title=\"near miss\">near miss</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonym:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/l%27%C3%A9chapper_belle#French\" title=\"l'échapper belle\">l'échapper belle</a></span></span></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Ouf, t'as <b>eu chaud</b> !</i> ―